From 3b8ac3a1aab53ac0d36450d821751afe8e254c60 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nathan <nathan@partly.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 21:53:26 +1200
Subject: [PATCH] Multi: quality trend charts, accuracy history, filter/sort
 tables, VIO on accuracy

- Quality: two line charts (classification + annotation over time) across
  all brands and snapshots, rendered as client component with recharts
- Quality: brand breakdown table replaced with interactive client component
  supporting search filter and sortable columns (VIO rank, brand, VIO %,
  classification, annotation, level)
- Accuracy: benchmarked brands table replaced with interactive client component
  supporting search filter and sortable columns; VIO rank + VIO % columns
  added, joined from quality snapshots by brand name; default sort by VIO rank
- Accuracy: new Snapshot Upload History section showing all benchmark uploads
  (brand, snapshot date, VINs, parts, accuracy, uploader, upload timestamp)
- Queries: getQualityTrendAllBrands(), getAccuracySnapshotHistory()
- getAllBrands() now joins VIO data from quality_brand_data by brand name

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
